name: No High and Up external vulnerabilities
description: No High and Up scored external vulnerability to be present in an analyzed project.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 0%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for any drop in code coverage.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 1%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 1%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 2%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 2%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 3%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 3%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 4%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 4%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 5%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 5%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 6%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 6%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 7%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 7%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 8%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 8%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 9%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 9%.

name: Code Coverage Will Not Drop By More Than 10%
description: Compares code coverage against the prior analysis, and checks for a drop in code coverage greater than 10%.

name: Dependencies Version Exist
description: Checks to ensure all dependencies have an explicit version defined instead of allowing latest to always be used.

name: High And Up Vulnerabilities < 1
description: No more than 1 High And Up scored vulnerability to be present in an analyzed project.

name: High And Up Vulnerabilities < 2
description: No more than 2 High And Up scored vulnerabilities to be present in an analyzed project.

name: High And Up Vulnerabilities < 3
description: No more than 3 High And Up scored vulnerabilities to be present in an analyzed project.

name: Code Coverage > 50%
description: The analyzed project must have greater than 50% code coverage.

name: Code Coverage > 60%
description: The analyzed project must have greater than 60% code coverage.

name: Code Coverage > 70%
description: The analyzed project must have greater than 70% code coverage.

name: Code Coverage > 80%
description: The analyzed project must have greater than 80% code coverage.

name: Code Coverage > 90%
description: The analyzed project must have greater than 90% code coverage.

name: Has a valid .about.yml file
description: The project source is required to include a valid .about.yml file.

name: Has a valid license file
description: The project source is required to include a valid license file.

name: Has no viruses
description: The project must not have any viruses found in the analysis.
